OL,3,CGovernment's flagship welfare bill at
OL,4,Crisk ahead of crunch vote next week
OL,6,FITV news has learned an amendment will
OL,7,Fbe tabled as early as Monday night to
OL,8,Fthe Government's flagship welfare
OL,9,Fbill, which could stop the legislation
OL,10,Fin its tracks.
OL,12,FThe amendment is expected to be tabled
OL,13,Fby Labour MP Meg Hillier, chair of
OL,14,Fboth the Treasury and Liaison
OL,15,Fcommittee, and signed by 12 additional
OL,16,FLabour party select committee chairs.
OL,18,FAt the time of writing, ITV News
OL,19,Funderstands the amendment has a total
OL,20,Fof 74 Labour MPs' names behind it.
