OL,4,Crisk ahead of crunch vote next week
OL,6,FThe amendment goes on to highlight the
OL,7,Flack of an impact assessment from the
OL,8,FOffice for Budget Responsibility and
OL,9,Fclaims, "the majority of the
OL,10,Fadditional employment support funding
OL,11,Fwill not be in place until the end of
OL,12,Fthe decade."
OL,14,FIn one particularly damning fact for
OL,15,Fthe government, this amendment calls
OL,16,Fout the government's own impact
OL,17,Fassessment which estimates, "250,000
OL,18,Fpeople will be pushed into poverty as
OL,19,Fa result of these provisions,
OL,20,Fincluding 50,000 children."
