OL,6,FThe Work and Pensions Secretary Liz
OL,7,FKendall addressed Labour MPs on Monday
OL,8,Fnight.
OL,10,FIn making her case for backing the
OL,11,Flegislation she is understood to have
OL,12,Ftold them: "Our plans are rooted in
OL,13,Ffairness ` for those who need support
OL,14,Fand for taxpayers.
OL,16,F"They are about ensuring the welfare
OL,17,Fstate survives, so there is always a
OL,18,Fsafety net for those who need it.
